{"tid":1760642,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[集中討論] ONEPIECE 海賊王 第964 話 漫畫情報","createTime":"2019-11-28T10:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T12:20:06.000Z","uid":130563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"89d0f509ddca0b35ebdba0ecbd93466f80438476","tid":1760642,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"964話標題 禦田的冒險<br />\n白鬍子拒絕讓禦田上船，但因為他太纏人了所以夜間出港離開。<br />\n禦田跳入海中，和追趕他的以藏一起雙雙被繩子抓（綁）住。<br />\n禦田仍然被拒絕，白鬍子只讓以藏上船。<br />\n白鬍子對憤怒的以藏說如果要讓我放棄就由你來說服吧。<br />\n約定如果他能忍耐三天就讓禦田上船。<br />\n剩下一小時的時候，禦田力氣用盡。<br />\n在沙灘被壞人糾纏的阿時遇到了傷痕累累的御田。<br />\n壞人暫時逃跑又再次出現，返回的白鬍子出手相救。<br />\n禦田、阿時和以藏上了白鬍子的船。<br />\n禦田很高興能夠環遊世界。<br />\n香克斯和巴基從報紙上得知白鬍子海賊團的活躍。<br />\n羅傑說想見見武士。"},{"pid":"7400d4d3599a45bda232e7017d680eb5fb239dd4","tid":1760642,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"以藏：我不會原諒你的，白鬍子！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/DoKeKSR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FDoKeKSR&h=d9ca2371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n時：我的年齡？26歲哦，出生是在&hellip;&hellip;xx年前左右吧<br />\n「什麼&mdash;&mdash;？！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/SZNIkmg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FSZNIkmg&h=e6ab6ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 大海賊 哥爾多&middot;羅傑<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/LmVBG9Z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FLmVBG9Z&h=68bbef93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴基：又是白鬍子的新聞，明明我們也搞事了！<br />\n「新來的和之國的武士，好像很亂來啊」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/lA7P0qN\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FlA7P0qN&h=0efc5e0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75934c78ffb2ee7706d9ca4315d8f0008af3d620","tid":1760642,"uid":144275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"終於真正開始講羅傑時代既大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7059b577de0c537066b25448ab71a